External knowledge for this question includes: 
- 'latest budget for each authority' means the budget with the highest allocation date for each authority; 
- 'more than two accesses' means the budget has been viewed or edited more than two times; 
- 'at least one audit' means there has been at least one update or delete operation on the budget; 
- 'allocated after January 1, 2020' means the budget's allocation date is after January 1, 2020.
